{
  "stem": "13851.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- the Nazi told them, they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of work were you forced to do during this time?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked-- OK, cleaning, like snow cleaning, or something in the kitchens for the Germans for helping out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all kinds, you know, manual work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there's only-- with me was the older brother from me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but the other brothers were married, and they lived separate, anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to do something, helping out with themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they wasn't working with us two together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They living in town, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not with us, the ghetto, because there were different people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us to work the factory, you know, the factory I used to work, they call it putting trains-- the train, where they go-- they do, those metal sides for the train.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we work on those train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd start [INAUDIBLE] with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, wood, whatever was bad things, we have to-- for fix it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's when they started working [? with ?] that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where they got me in the-- the factory working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we know if anybody's going to work for awhile, then meanwhile, they're going to need us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we'll-- we'll-- we won't survive, but for-- for a while, being interconnected, they need us, so they're not going to kill us out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's what then happened when they start taking out all the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll tell-- tell you what I told you about before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- let's see, that was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was about 15 years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, there's only brother that older from me, Sol, worked with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told you about that special oven, they make metal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's-- he was loading those, all kinds of material, for the oven.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
